Datasource.Parameter:
(SELECT way, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('water', 'bay') OR waterway IN ('riverbank') OR landuse = 'reservoir' ORDER BY z_order ASC, way_area DESC
) AS water
(SELECT way, ST_Area(way) AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE building IS NOT NULL) AS footprints

( SELECT place, name, (CASE WHEN population ~ E'^[[:digit:]]+$' THEN CAST (population AS INT) ELSE 0 END) AS population, name||'('||population||')' AS name_pop, way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE place IN ('city', 'town', 'village', 'hamlet') ORDER BY population DESC ) AS labels

(SELECT way, name, ST_Area(way) / 1000000 AS sq_km FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('water', 'bay') OR waterway IN ('riverbank') ORDER BY z_order ASC, way_area DESC
) AS water
( SELECT highway, name, way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway IN ('motorway', 'trunk', 'primary', 'secondary') ) AS labels
( SELECT highway, name, way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway IN ('tertiary', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'unclassified', 'service', 'minor') ) AS labels
